steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitmoduleapplelogin010" and Comment "Testing Module for Line Login"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitmoduleapplelogin010" display
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I add module "Line Login"
When I select multi dropdown has label "Associated users tables" with value "jitmoduleapplelogin010s"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Client ID" with value "jitera Client ID"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Secret Key" with value "jitera Secret Key"
When I collapse Header "Staging"
When I collapse Header "Development"
When I press Save button popover popup
Then I should see module "Line Login" was added by Edit button
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
Then I should see column with name "email" and index "4" of table name "jitmoduleapplelogin010" has type "string" display
Then I should see column with name "encrypted_password" and index "5" of table name "jitmoduleapplelogin010" has type "string" display
Then I should see column with name "password" and index "6" of table name "jitmoduleapplelogin010" has type "string" display
Then I should see column with name "password_confirmation" and index "7" of table name "jitmoduleapplelogin010" has type "string" display
When I open popup to see column infos Name "email" of table with Name "jitmoduleapplelogin010"
Then I should see checkbox popup Name "Required,Unique,Email" is disabled
Then I should see checkbox popup Name "Required,Unique,Email" is checked
When I close the modal popup
When I navigate to menu "API endpoints" with submenu "API endpoints editor"
Then I should see API screen display
When I wait query data API "jitmoduleapplelogin010s.email" is fetched completely
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitmoduleapplelogin010s/:id"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "","".
When I click tab "Response params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitmoduleapplelogin010s"
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "5" - value "email","Column Definition","email"
